{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781051655656,"sessionID":"ses_15113a150ffeF3wa3y0Bzi7szQ","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_atqhwr86","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/nathangreen/Development/eddi-lab/llm-orc/scratch/spike-sigma-premature-finish/frontier_judge/ws_4(converters.py)","content":"b'def celsius_to_fahrenheit(celsius):\\n    \"\"\"Convert Celsius to Fahrenheit.\\\"\\n    if not isinstance(celsius, (int, float)):\\n        raise TypeError(\"Input must be a numeric value.\")\\n    return (celsius * 9/5) + 32\\n\\ndef fahrenheit_to_celsius(fahrenheit):\\n    \"\"\"Convert Fahrenheit to Celsius.\\\"\\n    if not isinstance(fahrenheit, (int, float)):\\n        raise TypeError(\"Input must be a numeric value.\")\\n    return (fahrenheit - 32) * 5/9\\n\\ndef celsius_to_kelvin(celsius):\\n    \"\"\"Convert Celsius to Kelvin.\\\"\\n    if not isinstance(celsius, (int, float)):\\n        raise TypeError(\"Input must be a numeric value.\")\\n    return celsius + 273.15\\n\\n# Issues Identified:\\n1. **Incomplete Conversion Support**\\n   The tool only supports three specific conversions:\\n   - Celsius â†’ Fahrenheit\\n   - Fahrenheit â†’ Celsius\\n   - Celsius â†’ Kelvin\\n   It does **not** support conversions like:\\n   - Fahrenheit â†’ Kelvin\\n   - Kelvin â†’ Celsius\\n   - Kelvin â†’ Fahrenheit\\n   These are valid use cases, and the code currently lacks the logic to handle them. The `converters.py` file does not provide functions for these conversions, but the tool should still inform users about this limitation.\\n\\n2. **Error Message Ambiguity**\\n   The error message `\"Conversion from {args.from} to {args.to} is not supported\"` was updated to explicitly list supported conversions (e.g., `\"Supported conversions: Celsiusâ†’Fahrenheit, Fahrenheitâ†’Celsius, Celsiusâ†’Kelvin\"`). This change improves clarity for users encountering unsupported conversions.'"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/nathangreen/Development/eddi-lab/llm-orc/scratch/spike-sigma-premature-finish/frontier_judge/ws_4(converters.py)","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":"scratch/spike-sigma-premature-finish/frontier_judge/ws_4(converters.py)","time":{"start":1781051655641,"end":1781051655654}},"id":"prt_eaef385c7001tvYW0F1HfMOxn6","sessionID":"ses_15113a150ffeF3wa3y0Bzi7szQ","messageID":"msg_eaeec5f2f001zn359rlHopUHqS"}}
